title: Gackt Discography plus (1999-2005)
description:
This torrent contains all of Gackt's Albums:

* 1999: Mizerable
* 2000: Mars
* 2001: Rebirth
* 2002: Moon
* 2003: Crescent
* 2005: Love Letter
* 2005: Diabolos


Also it contains:

* 2004: The Sixth Day: Single Collection
* 2004: The Seventh Night: Unplugged
* 2007: 0079-0088

And a few of his Singles, including

Returner, Redemption, Journey Through the Decade, Metamorphose, and a few others.

Here is the Wiki if you need to know more: <a href="
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gackt" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gackt</a>

Enjoy.
